.Os HEIMDAL
.Sh NAME
.Nm hxtool
.Nd PKIX command-line utility
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Bk -words
.Oo Fl Fl version Oc
.Oo Fl Fl help Oc
.Op Ar sub-command
.Ek
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
