.Pp
Supported commands:
.Bl -tag -width Ds -offset indent
.It help
.It list-oids
.It verify
.It print
.It validate
.It certificate-copy, cc
.It ocsp-fetch
.It ocsp-verify
.It ocsp-print
.It revoke-print
.It generate-key
.It request-create
.It request-print
.It query
.It info
.It random-data
.It crypto-available
.It crypto-select
.It hex
.It certificate-sign, cert-sign, issue-certificate, ca
.It crl-sign
.El
Other sub-commands reported by the
